    <item>
      <title>🤫平均场近似与变分法｜Hartree, Fock, BCS能1:1:1混用吗？</title>
      <link>https://OkongOyangO.github.io/OkongOyangO.Notes/zh-cn/posts/mean_field_approximation/</link>
